 * {"wrapperType":"audiobook", "artistId":1036384314, "collectionId":1051433445, "amgArtistId":468749, "artistName":"Jack Johnson", "collectionName":"Anger Management: Anger Management Cure: Control Anger, Depression & Become Free (Unabridged)", "collectionCensoredName":"Anger Management: Anger Management Cure: Control Anger, Depression & Become Free (Unabridged)", "artistViewUrl":"https://books.apple.com/us/author/jack-johnson/id1036384314?uo=4", "collectionViewUrl":"https://books.apple.com/us/audiobook/anger-management-anger-management-cure-control-anger/id1051433445?uo=4", "artworkUrl60":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Music221/v4/0e/a3/47/0ea3471e-95af-743f-b35b-9ba61d7da1e7/rm_image.jpg/60x60bb.jpg", "artworkUrl100":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Music221/v4/0e/a3/47/0ea3471e-95af-743f-b35b-9ba61d7da1e7/rm_image.jpg/100x100bb.jpg", "collectionPrice":3.99, "collectionExplicitness":"cleaned", "trackCount":1, "copyright":"© 2015 Zac", "country":"USA", "currency":"USD", "releaseDate":"2015-10-05T07:00:00Z", "primaryGenreName":"Business & Personal Finance",
 * "previewUrl":"https://audio-ssl.itunes.apple.com/itunes-assets/AudioPreview113/v4/a9/92/d1/a992d1c3-1afa-234b-b0e4-f9d6a93317f0/mzaf_3322965638975966706.std.aac.p.m4a",
 * "description":"I want to take you on a journey of what anger is and how to conquer it or use it for good. Everyone has their own beliefs about what anger is and if it's good or bad. For 20 years of my life, I lived in fear, and that caused me to feel angry about my life. I was hanging around angry people, and I felt like I had no control. I worked out that most people who are depressed have repressed anger inside, and that's why they feel that way. <br /><br />This audiobook will give you back the power and control. I teach you how to release your anger so you can start living more free and healthily. If you sometimes get angry, it doesn't mean there's something wrong with you; it simply means you have something in your past that keeps getting triggered. It can all change in a heartbeat, and I will show you how to make the change in this book. <br /><br />We need to understand that every emotion we experience from day to day is useful in some context. People look at depression and anger like they are bad to experience. If you find the higher purpose to why it's happening, your life will transform. Take my hand on this journey, and your anger will soon be resolved. <br /><br />Take action today."},
 * {"wrapperType":"audiobook", "artistId":1036384314, "collectionId":1036383871, "amgArtistId":468749, "artistName":"Jack Johnson", "collectionName":"Anxiety: Overcome Anxiety, Social Anxiety, Shyness, Self Esteem & Insecurities (Unabridged)", "collectionCensoredName":"Anxiety: Overcome Anxiety, Social Anxiety, Shyness, Self Esteem & Insecurities (Unabridged)", "artistViewUrl":"https://books.apple.com/us/author/jack-johnson/id1036384314?uo=4", "collectionViewUrl":"https://books.apple.com/us/audiobook/anxiety-overcome-anxiety-social-anxiety-shyness-self/id1036383871?uo=4", "artworkUrl60":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Music60/v4/dd/56/f6/dd56f6fd-b957-7fa9-6807-4dbca11939a0/mzm.vwkbmchl.jpg/60x60bb.jpg", "artworkUrl100":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Music60/v4/dd/56/f6/dd56f6fd-b957-7fa9-6807-4dbca11939a0/mzm.vwkbmchl.jpg/100x100bb.jpg", "collectionPrice":5.99, "collectionExplicitness":"cleaned", "trackCount":1, "copyright":"© 2015 Zac Dixon", "country":"USA", "currency":"USD", "releaseDate":"2015-08-24T07:00:00Z", "primaryGenreName":"Business & Personal Finance",
 * "previewUrl":"https://audio-ssl.itunes.apple.com/itunes-assets/AudioPreview123/v4/22/28/27/2228279d-29eb-9559-cbaf-1944cdc10352/mzaf_8244289220768897884.std.aac.p.m4a",
 * "description":"Do you ever feel like you can't control your emotions and let them take over your life? Are you sick of feeling anxious pain in your own skin and letting your insecurities hold you back from enjoying life? <br /><br />For the last 15 years of my life, I have been searching for the best advice and tips that can significantly change a person from feeling insecure to completely confident. The reason I am passionate about this topic is because I used to struggle with severe anxiety and didn't know how to control my emotions. <br /><br />What I have learned over the last decade is that everyone experiences anxiety, but most people let it run their lives, and it makes you feel like you're not in control. I want to help you and give you all of the tips that can help you overcome your fears and start living the life you're truly meant to live. <br /><br />I know deep down there is a part of you that wants to change your life and really say \"enough is enough\" with feeling anxious. I will not hold back in this book and will give you the complete truth about what it takes to build yourself up and get out of any rut that you may be in. I have been at the lowest of lows and know exactly what it feels like; but just have faith that by the end of this book, life will never be the same again."},
